Microservices
A software architecture approach that addresses tight coupling by decoupling services, allowing them to operate independently.

Tight Coupling
A state where components have direct dependencies on others, leading to bottlenecks and fragility.

Generative AI
Generative AI is a type of artificial intelligence driven by deep learning, capable of generating text, images, and videos by generalizing across diverse datasets.

Deep Learning
Deep learning is a method that drives Generative AI, enabling it to learn from vast, diverse datasets.
